                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="candidate-workflow-stage offered">
                            <div class="candidate-workflow-substage" sub-stage="1">
                                <div>Application is in <strong>Offered</strong> stage.</div>
                                We're waiting for applicant's response.
